high_descs: Turn around and go near the bowl.
Take the bowl from the box.
Placed the bowl into the sink.
Turn around and go near the sink.
There is a potato in the fridge.
Take the potato from the refrigerator.
Placed the potato into the bowl in the sink.
Turn around and go near the potato bowl.
There is a knife in the fridge.
Then take a butterknife from the refrigerator.
Turn around and go near the potato.
Using the knife, slice the potato into pieces.
anns.task_desc: Collect Potato, Bowl, Knife, and slice the potatoes in SinkBasin.

high_descs: Turn around to face the bowl.
Pick up the bowl from the box.
Turn around and walk up to face the larger sink on the counter.
Put the bowl in the sink.
Turn right to face the fridge.
Pick up the potato from the fridge.
Turn around to face the larger bowl.
Put the potato in the bowl.
Turn left to head back to the fridge.
Pick up the butterknife from the fridge.
Walk back to the larger potato sink.
Slice the potato into pieces.
anns.task_desc: Slice potato in the bowl in the SinkBasin.

high_descs: Turn around and go towards the nearby bowl on the ground.
Pick up the silver bowl from inside the box.
Walk along the counters towards the sink.
Put the bowl into the sink.
Turn right towards the fridge.
Remove the potato from the fridge.
Turn back towards the bowl.
Place the potato into the bowl in the sink.
Turn back towards the fridge.
Remove the butterknife from the fridge.
Turn back towards the potato.
Slice up the potato in the bowl.
anns.task_desc: Slice up a Potato in a Bowl in a SinkBasin.
